'''Elle Kingsley''' is a police officer who attended the firefighters' training.

==History==
Elle is one of the officers who came to the training held by the firefighters of Station 19. She was put in a group run by Jack and Maya, both of whom were attracted to her. They spent the day flirting with her and trying to impress her and prove they were better than the other. At the end of the day, Jack and Maya both got her number.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
While working with [[Maya Bishop]] and [[Jack Gibson]], she flirted with both and gave each of them her phone number.

==Career==
She is a police officer with the Seattle Metropolitan Police Department.

==Notes and Trivia==
*She gets up at 4 A.M. to run.
*She loves being on the water.
